headline: Robinhood Markets (HOOD) Releases Jan 2026 Operating Data
summary: Robinhood Markets, Inc. (NASDAQ:HOOD) is one of the Most Promising Stocks to Invest In Before They Take Off. On February 19, Robinhood Markets, Inc. (NASDAQ:HOOD) released its January 2026 operating data. The company reported that funded customers for the month reached 27.2 million, representing an increase of 190,000 from December 2025 and 1.75 million year-over-year. […]
